@page "/components/TyneButton"
@layout ComponentLayout<TyneButton>

<DocsTextBlock>
    <code>@nameof(TyneButton)</code> behaves identically to the <code>@nameof(MudButton)</code>,
    except it is <code>@nameof(MudButton.Disabled)</code> while the <code>@nameof(MudButton.OnClick)</code>
    callback is being executed.
</DocsTextBlock>

