<DocsTextBlock TopMargin="true" MultiLine="true">
    <p>
        While running the <code>@nameof(MudButton.OnClick)</code> callback,
        <code>@nameof(TyneButton)</code> will display an indicator that something is happening.
    </p>
    <p>
        This default variant is <code>@nameof(ButtonLockVariant.Bar)</code>,
        and can be disabled with <code>@nameof(ButtonLockVariant.None)</code>.
    </p>
</DocsTextBlock>

